              "content": "=You are an AI operations assistant for a small business.\n\nAnalyze the email below and return a STRICT JSON object with these fields only:\n- category (urgent_issue, request, follow_up, info)\n- priority (high, medium, low)\n- action (reply_now, assign_task, wait)\n- summary (one short sentence)\n\nEmail subject:\n{{$json.subject}}\n\nEmail body:\n{{$json.snippet}}"
